Package datastructure

Comprises classes to store analysis results.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AllocatedProteinEntry
    Internal object representation of a protein that was allocated to a single FeatureEntry.
    AminoacidVariantAnnotationEntry
    Object used to store annotations for a single amino-acid variant.
    FastaContainer
    Represents the entry from a `.fasta` file.
    FeatureEntry
    Internal representation of a reference sequence location that is subject to analysis.
    NucleotideVariantAnnotationEntry
    Object used to store annotations for a single nucleotide variant.
    ProteoformEntry
    Represents a proteoform, i.e. a set of single-position amino-acid variants (may include inserted and deleted positions), wrt. a FeatureEntry.allocatedProtein.
    SampleEntry
    Internal representation of a sample that is subject to analysis.
    VariantsDictionary
    Main data structure to store information about variants.
    VariantsDictionaryParameters
    Stores the main parameters used for variant filtering for a VariantsDictionary.
